1
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,280
Qingxue.

2
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,400
Qingxue, wake up.

3
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,400
Qingxue.

4
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,480
Qingxue, can you hear me?

5
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,840
Why isn't it working at a time like this?

6
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,480
Wu Ming.

7
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,680
Stay calm.

8
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:02,760
Right.

9
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,560
Don't panic.

10
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,680
Qingxue is in serious danger now.

11
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,319
Could you boil some water for me

12
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,280
and prepare the medicine?

13
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:10,319
What do we do now?

14
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:10,759
Don't panic.

15
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:31,560
Why is she the only one you see?

16
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,960
Lu Tanxiang.

17
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:35,400
You'll never escape the Lu Family.

18
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,639
Even in death,

19
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:40,319
you'll be buried beneath the Lu memorial tablets.

20
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:42,039
Yang Yunfan

21
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:44,520
will never give you a second glance.

22
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:47,639
A weakling like you doesn't exist in his world.

23
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,120
You're just a lowly Apothecary.

24
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,240
What could you possibly mean to him?

25
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,600
Qingxue.

26
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,240
Actually,

27
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,439
you're not so bad to look at.

28
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,839
Qingxue, hold on.

29
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:34,399
Just one more dose

30
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:35,199
and you'll be fine.

31
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,240
You can't let anything happen to you.

32
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,160
I'm worried sick.

33
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,800
It's okay.

34
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,800
Wu Ming.

35
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,040
Here.

36
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,639
Slowly.

37
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,079
How are you?

38
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,199
Feeling any better?

39
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,079
Qingxue?

40
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,040
A bit dizzy.

41
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,319
A bit dizzy.

42
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,240
That's not right.

43
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:16,920
The medicine I prepared was...

44
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,160
Qingxue!

45
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,199
Qingxue!

46
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:25,560
How could this happen?

47
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,519
The toxin has mutated.

48
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,759
This shouldn't be possible.

49
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,879
What did you do?

50
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,399
I just wanted you to see me.

51
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:57,079
You weren't like this when we met.

52
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,360
Why would you do this?

53
00:05:59,079 --> 00:05:59,720
You don't understand.

54
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,720
I had no choice.

55
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,800
You always say you had no choice.

56
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:07,000
How long will you cling to your insecurity

57
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,399
and your victim complex?

58
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,079
What do you know?

59
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:11,839
With parents like mine,

60
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:13,199
what was I supposed to do?

61
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:15,439
Nothing I do is ever right.

62
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:17,079
I'll always live in my brother's shadow.

63
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:18,600
Even after he was taken,

64
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,839
I'm just a stand-in until he returns.

65
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,839
You always blame fate,

66
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,519
blame your background.

67
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,680
You think that gives you

68
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,920
the right to hurt others without consequence?

69
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,759
You never needed me.

70
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,720
You have to look within yourself.

71
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,600
If you don't change,

72
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,680
nothing will.

73
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,199
I knew it.

74
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,319
You won't forgive me.

75
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,319
Stop right there!

76
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,839
Did you think you could escape?

77
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:15,079
Your every move is under my control.

78
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,000
Father.

79
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,839
You've been watching me?

80
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,839
If I didn't keep an eye on you,

81
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,319
you useless thing,

82
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,920
what could you ever accomplish?

83
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,399
But I'm your daughter.

84
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:44,199
I'm not your puppet.

85
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:46,240
Who am I doing this for?

86
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,800
It's all for you,

87
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,879
for the Lu Family.

88
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:08,480
We're here.

89
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,199
Come on.

90
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,120
Qingxue.

91
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,720
I'll go find the medicine first.

92
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:24,879
I'll be right back.

93
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,759
You rest here for a bit.

94
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,759
Promise me.

95
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:28,639
Don't fall asleep, okay?

96
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,559
Yunfan.

97
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,759
Yunfan.

98
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,919
Yunfan.

99
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,360
I'm sorry.

100
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,559
I've been a burden to you.

101
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,279
You know,

102
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,799
once all this is over,

103
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:50,480
you owe me the most lavish engagement banquet.

104
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,000
Okay, got it.

105
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,879
Silly.

106
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,559
Got it.

107
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,440
Qingxue.

108
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,480
You have to pull through.

109
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,840
The scent of the Purple Sun Flower.

110
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,639
I don't think we need to wait any longer.

111
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:03,039
They're not coming back.

112
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,440
I'm the only one who's gathered all the herbs

113
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,039
and cured the patient.

114
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,679
The outcome is already obvious.

115
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,679
Time isn't up yet.

116
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:17,120
How do you know they won't come?

117
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:19,080
I believe they'll definitely come.

118
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:20,799
Xiangyang.

119
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:21,840
Don't be impatient.

120
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,000
The outcome is set.

121
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,320
Why rush it now?

122
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,879
Once you become Medicine Master,

123
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,399
you can't be this hot-headed.

124
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:33,320
Then we'll wait until time runs out.

125
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:50,679
Yang Yunfan and Ye Qingxue are here.

126
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:24,600
Not too early, not too late

127
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:25,799
Right on time

128
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:35,080
What?

129
00:11:35,639 --> 00:11:36,639
surprised to see

130
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,600
the two of us here?

131
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,000
Qingxue can be saved.

132
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,799
Cutting it awfully close, aren't you?

133
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:52,159
What a pity.

134
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:53,759
You didn't bring the main herb.

135
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:55,759
It's no different from not showing up.

136
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,120
Li Chiyao,

137
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,840
how can your imagination be so limited?

138
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,879
Who said I didn't bring the main herb?

139
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,720
Ghost Needle Grass.

140
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,519
Impossible!

141
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,080
Are you wearing reading glasses or what?

142
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,440
Li Chiyao can't even identify an herb.

143
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,519
Why even compete in the Path of Healing?

144
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:30,960
Yang Yunfan, Li Chiyao,

145
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,879
this contest is about the medicine's effect,

146
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,559
not who arrives first.

147
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,519
Yang Yunfan,

148
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:38,879
since you've arrived,

149
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,120
prepare to continue the contest.

150
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,000
Chief Pharmacist Lu,

151
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,240
please distribute the auxiliary herbs.

152
00:13:43,799 --> 00:13:44,159
Yes.

153
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,080
Mystic Water Hall's Chief Pharmacist Lu,

154
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:02,399
now handing out herbs like an Apothecary?

155
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,879
Son-in-law.

156
00:14:50,039 --> 00:14:50,960
What are you doing?
